author: scottbw
msg: Changed the behaviour of preferences such that a request for a non-existing preference returns undefined instead of null; also calling clear or removeItem on a preference deletes it rather than setting it to null. This enables us to pass the "au" conformance test for W3C Widgets: Widget Interface (see http://dev.w3.org/2006/waf/widgets-api/test-suite/)
